  <summary date="2021-09-24T16:20:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Firearm Due Process Protection Act

This bill revises the hearing procedure and remedy for an individual who (1) was denied a firearm due to erroneous information provided by a state or the National Instant Criminal Background Check System concerning the individual, or (2) was denied a firearm but was not prohibited from receiving a firearm.</summary>
